# 🔄 Kansas Frontier Matrix — **Hazards Transformation Layer**  
`data/work/tmp/hazards/transforms/`

**Mission:** Perform **CF/CRS harmonization, reprojection, and FAIR+CARE metadata validation** across all hazard datasets — tornado, flood, wildfire, and drought — ensuring consistent, explainable, and reproducible transformations.

