## 🧮 FAIR+CARE Transformation Matrix

| FAIR Dim. | CARE Dim. | Artifact | Purpose | Reference |
|:--|:--|:--|:--|:--|
| **Findable** | Collective Benefit | `transform_manifest.json` | Trace lineage between source & output | FAIR F1 |
| **Accessible** | Responsibility | `cf_fix_logs.json` | Document all metadata harmonizations | FAIR A2 |
| **Interoperable** | Ethics | `reprojection_trace.log` | Ensure CRS consistency across domains | FAIR I3 |
| **Reusable** | Equity | `transform_checksums.json` | Guarantee reproducibility and verifiability | FAIR R1 |

