## 🧠 Transformation Workflow Overview

```mermaid
flowchart TD
A[Hazard Data (staging/)] --> B[CF/FAIR Metadata Validation]
B --> C[Reprojection to EPSG:4326]
C --> D[Spatial Resampling + COG Conversion]
D --> E[Checksum Verification + FAIR Validation]
E --> F[Governance Ledger Registration]
```

