## 🧬 CF Metadata Alignment Policy

- Global attributes required: `title`, `institution`, `source`, `history`, `references`, `license`.  
- CF variables standardized with SI units and consistent names.  
- Spatial axes: `lat`, `lon`, temporal axis `time` (ISO-8601 UTC).  
- All metadata updates logged to `cf_fix_logs.json` with timestamps, diffs, and user signatures.

